{"id":602901,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/01/【立此存照】习近平的新年贺词2019的第一份禁/","date":"2019-01-02T06:02:52Z","modified":"2019-01-02T06:02:52Z","title":"【立此存照】“习近平的新年贺词”2019的第一份禁评","content":"<p>近日，有网友发现，“<a href=\"http://www.xinhuanet.com/politics/2018-12/31/c_1123931806.htm\">习近平2019新年贺词完整版</a>”在新浪微博与B站都被限制了评论：</p>\n<blockquote><p>以人民日报<a href=\"https://weibo.com/2803301701/H9NYT3zAn?type=comment#_rnd1546408316729\">微博</a>为例，该视频转发的微博下有2400余条网友评论，却只能显示显示90余条被筛选出的“热门评论”，无法显示其他网友的实时评论：</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/习近平2019新年贺词完整视频习.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-602906\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/习近平2019新年贺词完整视频习.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"643\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/习近平2019新年贺词完整视频习.png 783w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/习近平2019新年贺词完整视频习-210x300.png 210w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/习近平2019新年贺词完整视频习-768x1098.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/习近平2019新年贺词完整视频习-717x1024.png 717w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>以B站为例，共青团中央所发布的<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/av39556953?from=search&amp;seid=14927906584087913233\">习近平新年贺词</a>被完全关闭了网友评论以及弹幕，成为了真正意义的“禁评”。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-602907\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/Dv1Zf5AU0AAYUar.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"799\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/Dv1Zf5AU0AAYUar.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/Dv1Zf5AU0AAYUar-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/Dv1Zf5AU0AAYUar-577x1024.jpg 577w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/习近平2019新年贺词完整视频2.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-602908\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/习近平2019新年贺词完整视频2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"277\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/习近平2019新年贺词完整视频2.png 1266w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/习近平2019新年贺词完整视频2-300x184.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/习近平2019新年贺词完整视频2-768x472.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/习近平2019新年贺词完整视频2-1024x629.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/习近平2019新年贺词完整视频2-80x48.png 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<blockquote><p><a title=\"【敏感词库】斗鱼账号注册禁用词：倒吸\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/12/%e3%80%90%e6%95%8f%e6%84%9f%e8%af%8d%e5%ba%93%e3%80%91%e6%96%97%e9%b1%bc%e8%b4%a6%e5%8f%b7%e6%b3%a8%e5%86%8c%e7%a6%81%e7%94%a8%e8%af%8d%ef%bc%9a%e5%80%92%e5%90%b8/\">【敏感词库】斗鱼账号注册禁用词：倒吸</a></p>\n<p><a title=\"【敏感词库】习狗、开倒车 2018.12.13\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/12/%e3%80%90%e6%95%8f%e6%84%9f%e8%af%8d%e5%ba%93%e3%80%91%e4%b9%a0%e7%8b%97%e3%80%81%e5%bc%80%e5%80%92%e8%bd%a6/\">【敏感词库】习狗、开倒车</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/11/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91b%e7%ab%99%e5%bc%80%e5%80%92%e8%bd%a6%e8%a7%86%e9%a2%91%e7%ba%b7%e7%ba%b7%e7%a6%81%e8%af%84/\">【立此存照】B站“开倒车”视频纷纷“禁评”</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/07/%e5%a2%99%e5%a4%96%e6%a5%bc-%e5%8f%b8%e6%9c%ba%e5%9c%a8%e9%ab%98%e9%80%9f%e4%b8%8a%e5%bc%80%e5%80%92%e8%bd%a6-%e8%a2%ab%e8%bf%bd%e5%b0%be%e5%8f%91%e7%94%9f%e6%83%a8%e5%89%a7/\">墙外楼 | 司机在高速上开倒车 被追尾发生惨剧</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/06/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e4%ba%ba%e6%b0%91%e7%bd%91%e5%88%a0%e9%99%a4%e9%80%94%e8%a7%82tg%e5%bc%80%e5%80%92%e8%bd%a6%e4%b8%8b%e5%8f%b0%e5%be%ae/\">【立此存照】人民网删除“途观(TG)开倒车下台”微博</a></p></blockquote>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,2794